      <text x="20" y="20" fill="var(--muted)" font-size="11" font-family="Lora,serif">Narrow</text>
      <text x="340" y="20" text-anchor="end" fill="var(--muted)" font-size="11" font-family="Lora,serif">Broad</text>
      <rect x="20" y="34" width="320" height="13" rx="6.5" fill="url(#laysg)" opacity="0.9"/>
      <g transform="translate(118,40.5)"><line x1="0" y1="-15" x2="0" y2="15" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="0" cy="0" r="6" fill="var(--ink)" stroke="var(--card)" stroke-width="2"/></g>
      <text x="118" y="76" text-anchor="middle" fill="var(--ink)" font-size="11.5" font-family="Fraunces,serif" font-weight="600">Today — records on top, thin underneath</text>
    </svg></div>
    <figcaption>The index is at highs, but participation is narrow — fewer stocks are carrying more weight. <span class="dconf medium">medium confidence</span></figcaption>
  </figure>
  </div>
</div></section>

